# LLM experiments, to use the power of LLM for search



## Getting started

In order to test the experiments yourself please download the latest version of Tampermonkey: https://www.tampermonkey.net/
When you have installed the browserplugin, you may copy/past the JS scripts in this repository or use the import functionality in Tampermonkey to receive updates as well.


## Name
LLM-experiments: use the power of LLM for search enhancement



## Description
The goal of this project is to learn and test serveral ways of using LLM models out there, to gain for the current bol website.

Currenlty we are testing with:
- OpenAI, gpt-4 /completions
- Cohere, command-r-plus /chat


