## Background
In finding a way to show the power of LLM's we had a brainstorm with our HMF department. After a short conclusion at the end of the session we are looking into the "low hanging fruit" where end customers can benefit from. In order to get from a creative idea to the next stage we need to figure out several questions.



## Prompts
1. "Geef een alternatieve suggestie om producten te vinden voor de volgende woorden, die te gebruiken bij een Nederlandse e-commerce website: + zoekterm +
1. "Geef me één zoekterm als alternatieve suggestie om producten mee te vinden op een Nederlandse e-commerce website voor de volgende zoekterm: " + zoekterm + " (antwoord alleen met de zoekterm)

## Test cases
In order to learn if there is value in a suggetion like this one we would love to test with internatioals

For example: the top searches that Brazilians do and got some results:
- fone de ouvido sem fio (wireless headphones / earbuds)
- geladeira (fridge)
- sandalia feminina (women sandaals)
- árvore de natal (christmas tree)
- material escolar (school supplies)
- mochila infantil (kid's backpack)
- ar-condicionado (airconditioning)

